com.here.android.mpa.mapping

Class MapProxyObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.common.ViewObject
      • com.here.android.mpa.mapping.MapProxyObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterViewObject, MapBuildingObject, MapCartoMarker, SafetySpotObject, TrafficEventObject, TransitAccessObject, TransitLineObject, TransitLineSegmentObject, TransitStopObject

    public abstract class MapProxyObject
extends ViewObject
    Represents a base interface for all view objects rendered as part of the map. A proxy object may contain special information depending on its type (for example, TransitStopObject may provide transit stop-related information), but it cannot be created or modified.

    This interface serves as a generalization for several more specified proxy object types, bundling their common properties.
